The paper discusses the use of deep learning in computer vision for intelligent video analysis, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the challenges of large-scale video data management, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the need for standardization, which could fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
